metadata.name: Queen of Cake Land/ケーキの国の女王
metadata.description:
Queen of Cake Land

She has been crowned Queen of the Land of Cakes and will serve for the peace and prosperity of the country.
Her smiling face and stately demeanor have been deeply engraved as a symbol of peace among the people.

ケーキの国の女王に即位した彼女は、この国の安寧と繁栄のため奉仕します。
女王の微笑む姿と堂々とした態度は国民に平和の象徴として深く刻まれました。

・About the work
The theme of this year's exhibition was "Queen of the Land of Cakes.
I love frills, ribbons, and other pretty materials, and I have always loved to express the details of clothing, so I paid particular attention to this work.
The queen's crown is in the shape of a cream aperture, and the scepter she holds in her hand is a cake fork.
The dress incorporates the delicate patterns on the cake.
The lace and other patterns were hand-drawn one by one.
Please take a look at the details of the work.
